1077
01:22:05,546 --> 01:22:07,505
<i>They report his condition as critical.</i>

1078
01:22:08,674 --> 01:22:10,633
He's not expected to survive.

1079
01:22:13,012 --> 01:22:14,178
Jim.

1080
01:22:15,848 --> 01:22:17,307
