01:25:02,014 --> 01:25:04,182
Drilling holes in his head
is not the answer.

1128
01:25:04,266 --> 01:25:06,100
The artery must be repaired.

1129
01:25:06,185 --> 01:25:08,770
Now put away your butcher knives
and let me save this patient

