1367
01:51:45,532 --> 01:51:46,949
Don't worry.

1368
01:51:48,035 --> 01:51:49,535
l'll find you.

1369
01:51:55,250 --> 01:51:57,293
See you around the galaxy.

1370
01:52:12,101 --> 01:52:13,309
Father.

1371
01:52:13,977 --> 01:52:18,106
